outputs.output_descr:
The overall objective is to assist the Palestinian Authority (PA), through the local aid coordination structure, in the coordination of activities related to governance and, in particular, to provide strategic, analytical and coordination input to the Governance Strategy Group (GSG), the Sector Working Groups (SWGs) under its umbrella and to the Ministry of Planning and Administrative Development.

In specific, the action aims to achieve the following objectives:
•	Improved and continuous coordination of the Governance Strategy Group and the formal and informal aid coordination forums under its umbrella;
•	Strengthened capacities in the governance sector within MoPAD (and counterparts at governance related line ministries);
•	Strengthened aid effectiveness capacities within MoPAD;
